    {
      "id": "9a437d4f_536c0bd0",
      "file_path": "controlloop/common/guard/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/guard/PolicyGuardXacmlHelper.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 435,
      "message": "This do not exist in our environment.\n\nYou can get environment properties from\n\nPolicyEngine.manage.getEnvironmentProperty(\"SQL_HOST\")\nPolicyEngine.manage.getEnvironmentProperty(\"sql.db.username\")\nPolicyEngine.manage.getEnvironmentProperty(\"sql.db.password\")\n\nThese are from here:\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/drools-applications/tree/controlloop/packages/basex/src/files/config/controlloop.properties.environment\n\nThe SQL_HOST is not in this file, but it is already available to you.  I will add an entry on the above mentioned file at some point for \"sql.db.host\" but is not relevant for this purpose.\n\nWith the previous information you can compose the jdbc url.  The drive is always \"mariadb\".",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2017-09-27 16:27:27.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "9a437d4f_d87498ff",
      "file_path": "controlloop/common/guard/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/guard/Util.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 42,
      "message": "The names should be taken from here:\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/drools-applications/tree/controlloop/packages/basex/src/files/config/controlloop.properties.environment\n\nthese are the relevant env names for guard:\n\npdpx.host=${{PDP_HOST}}\npdpx.username={{PDP_USERNAME}}\npdpx.password={{PDP_PASSWORD}}\npdpx.environment={{PDP_ENVIRONMENT}}\npdpx.client.username={{PDP_CLIENT_USERNAME}}\npdpx.client.password={{PDP_CLIENT_PASSWORD}}\n\nguard.url=http://${{PDP_HOST}}:8081/pdp/api/getDecision\nguard.jdbc.url=mariadb://${{SQL_HOST}}:3306/operationshistory10",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2017-09-27 16:27:27.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
