      "line": 45,
      "message": "see my comments on patch set 1.\n\nThis exists.   These are the ones that should be used per this file.\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/drools-applications/tree/controlloop/packages/basex/src/files/config/controlloop.properties.environment\n\nthe pdpx and the guard ones are the ones of interest.",
